&lt;p>Initially, the Upanishads went over me.&lt;br>
Then, I went over the Upanishads -&lt;br>
a journey spanning roughly 20 years.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Now, reading self-help books or &lt;br>
even religious texts feels like reading children’s books.&lt;br>
They are good, engaging, but the truth lies elsewhere.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>If someone asks me&lt;br>
what I have learned after reading so much,&lt;br>
contemplating so deeply,&lt;br>
on both worldly and inner sciences,&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Value Based True Friendship</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/wiaposts/value-based-true-friendship/</link><pubDate>Mon, 31 Aug 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/wiaposts/value-based-true-friendship/</guid><description>&lt;p>
